13. CONCLUSION
The One Step Challenge system provides an optimal balance between trader flexibility and firm protection. Through adaptive rules, dynamic pricing, and comprehensive monitoring, the system delivers:
•	Rapid evaluation completion (5-10 days)
•	Maximum configuration flexibility
•	Intelligent risk-based pricing
•	Automated rule adaptation
•	Comprehensive progress tracking
•	5× scaling opportunity
The adaptive nature of the system ensures that each configuration is fairly priced and appropriately monitored, creating a sustainable and profitable evaluation model that scales with trader success.
